    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>

    <p>         
        This site is <b>not affiliated with monday.com</b> in any way. If you have any concerns about using this site, please just use
        <a target="_blank" href="https://monday.com/marketplace/" rel="nofollow">monday.com marketplace</a> instead.
